  "1358710": {
    "name": "Battle Cry of Freedom",
    "steam_appid": 1358710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/ab1adfe0c99c47e26a7c8dedec4a5cb7.avif?t=1723617387\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br> <br><i>自由战吼的游戏背景以 19 世纪的美国南北战争为舞台，让玩家们有机会亲身成为美国北军或南军的一员，体验令人屏息的第一人称与第三人称的激烈实时战斗。</i><br> <br>本游戏有着广泛的武器可供玩家选择，从经典的滑膛枪到令人生畏的火炮。还有残酷且致命的近战工具诸如刺刀、匕首和军刀任君选择，供您在血腥的美利坚战场上取得先机。<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/d5bb7f2fa5e37766025acbd0203bcdf9.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/d5bb7f2fa5e37766025acbd0203bcdf9.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/d5bb7f2fa5e37766025acbd0203bcdf9.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超大规模的多人战场</h2>置身于超大规模的战场与高达 500 名玩家同时在一个完全可破坏的真实美国内战环境中同场竞技。<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/0f2e077a23eeec964e7022d4e86199e0.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/0f2e077a23eeec964e7022d4e86199e0.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/0f2e077a23eeec964e7022d4e86199e0.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更庞大的领军模式</h2>率领 <strong>由 AI 组成</strong> 的兵团，带领部队赢得荣耀。每个服务器上最高可以同时支持多达 800 个机器人的超大规模领军作战，这将是展现您谋略的终极战场。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找出适合自己的玩法</h2><strong>应征入伍成为步兵</strong><br>成为一名线列中的普通士兵，还是成为神射手兵团的一员跻身精英行列，亦或是想成为军乐手为队伍传递指令，这都取决于您的选择。探索并体验军队中的各种角色，亲自找出适合自己的独特玩法。<br><br> <br><strong>或是在炮兵部队中服役</strong><br>成为一名令人生畏的炮兵，在部队后方支援队伍粉碎敌人的层层抵抗。加入重炮兵部队，使用 100 磅帕罗特线膛炮为敌军阵地带去毁灭。<br><br><strong>加入骑兵</strong><br>加入骑兵部队并冲入战场，通过在战场上快速高效的机动来支持步兵。 挥舞着致命的连发步枪，消灭任何胆敢挡在你路上的敌人。<br> <br><strong>作为一名专家加入战场</strong><br>成为工兵，通过修建防御工事、架设浮桥以及输送弹药补给成为团队坚固的后盾。或是成为一名战地外科医师，帮助受到重伤的友军脱离险情。您皆可自由选择。<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/fd04468fb0ebbd33d43aa5f51481cfbd.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/fd04468fb0ebbd33d43aa5f51481cfbd.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/fd04468fb0ebbd33d43aa5f51481cfbd.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >琳琅满目的军火库</h2>为自己寻找风格。滑膛炮、步枪、手枪、剑、斧头…应有尽有，有超过120把独特的老家伙待您挑选，70 种不同的弹药类型和 20 多种火炮，看您的心情自由选择。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >上刺刀——冲锋！</h2>装上刺刀冲上前线。使用基于方向的近战格斗系统击溃您的敌人，这是一个受到《骑马与砍杀：战团》启发的战斗系统。新玩家们能够轻松入门，然而却需要千锤百炼才能成为一名大师。<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/a284da4e35e59a53fb7b2d377af4d049.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/a284da4e35e59a53fb7b2d377af4d049.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/a284da4e35e59a53fb7b2d377af4d049.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于现实逻辑开发的弹丸物理系统</h2>自由战吼真实的模拟了现实世界中的子弹物理，不仅仅是模拟了射速和扭率，我们甚至还考究了湿度、温度、空气密度、本地重力、风向和风力对子弹的影响。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进阶的火炮玩法</h2>多达 20 门火炮供玩家使用，并且每门火炮都有着自己独一无二的性能与优缺点。<strong>火炮可以装入多种类型的炮弹，</strong>从普通炮弹到撞击式引信弹、时间引信炮弹、实心炮弹、锡罐弹和霰弹等，并且有着如同它们名称一样的效果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/c8bf395f2f3b71e418615c0133aa74c9.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/c8bf395f2f3b71e418615c0133aa74c9.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/c8bf395f2f3b71e418615c0133aa74c9.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >火车、汽船等</h2>操作装甲列车、汽船和木制汽艇，提供穿越战场的新方式。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >骑马作战</h2>骑上你可信赖的战马，投入战斗。 用你的连发步枪以致命的准确性击败你的敌人，或者用你的重型骑兵军刀杀死他们！ 拖曳火炮穿越战场以获得更大的机动性。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/d908564f232e5b9454c018c31f6a626e.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/d908564f232e5b9454c018c31f6a626e.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/d908564f232e5b9454c018c31f6a626e.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可摧毁的环境</h2>在自由战吼的战场中，<strong>一切瞬息万变。</strong>在游戏中，摧毁桥梁、弄倒树木、往墙上打洞或是炸毁障碍物都是可以的。对了，玩家们可不要试着站在一颗即将要倒的树下面喔，否则后果……<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/867298de98b8dc696d2e8fcb0934607f.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/867298de98b8dc696d2e8fcb0934607f.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/867298de98b8dc696d2e8fcb0934607f.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造，摧毁，补给</h2>玩家可以扮演战地工兵，<strong>在战场上建造多种防御工事</strong>，比如布置沙袋掩体或是拒马。又可以在前线上部署重生点，给友军<strong>补充武器弹药</strong>成为团队坚实的后盾。您也可以带头冲锋，用<strong>炸药桶</strong>把敌人的碉堡炸出窟窿或是用您的伐木斧拆掉敌方的工事。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/6d8a6afed0edf69f11e6a99a493f3aad.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/6d8a6afed0edf69f11e6a99a493f3aad.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/6d8a6afed0edf69f11e6a99a493f3aad.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为角色定制外观</h2>展现你的着装品味，自定义角色的制服甚至是袜子的颜色。<strong>从数以千计的具有历史还原准确性的制服</strong>和装备中挑选，还是从不同的鞋子，外套和帽子等等中拼搭出独特个性。噢，甚至您还可以决定怎么穿外套，敞开穿还是合上穿，亦或是穿在里面还是穿在外面…<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/abf1547e29db0b6f65c7a61b0a8e0562.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/abf1547e29db0b6f65c7a61b0a8e0562.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/abf1547e29db0b6f65c7a61b0a8e0562.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >举枪 - 敬礼！</h2>自由战吼中的所有角色动画都力求还原真实，我们<strong>参考了历史上的练兵手册</strong>《Casey's Infantry Tactics》《Hardee's Revised》等。除去一些常规的“游戏”动作，动画都试图还原历史准确性，本游戏也提供了大量的“角色扮演”动画让玩家感受内战时代风貌融入背景，提供多种的举枪、敬礼，稍息和泊枪的姿势。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >历史还原准确性</h2><strong>游戏玩法受到真实历史的启发</strong>，我们只在创造出一个更具吸引力和更振奋的游戏体验时才会做出改变。自由战吼尽管并不是一款美国内战历史模拟器，但是涉及到一些用来“看的”外观上的东西时我们<strong>毫无妥协</strong>，例如 3D 模型和角色动画，每条纫痕都几近还原！<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/2916319dffe8a7e5ceffb138f93aeef3.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/2916319dffe8a7e5ceffb138f93aeef3.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/2916319dffe8a7e5ceffb138f93aeef3.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过 14 个战场待您探索</h2>游玩<strong> 14 张手工打造的地图</strong>，地图灵感都取材自真实世界中的地点和历史上真实存在过的战场。玩家们也可以在<strong>自动生成的地图</strong>中探索，每次游玩都可以提供完全不同的战斗环境。<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/6282665300af3043868914c319305020.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/6282665300af3043868914c319305020.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/6282665300af3043868914c319305020.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态天气和昼夜循环</h2>在千变万化的战场上作战！<strong>大风和雷电会摧毁树木</strong>，雨和雾会降低能见度，大风能够影响子弹轨迹。自由战吼游戏具有<strong>动态天气</strong>、风、季节与昼夜循环功能。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/50df058d467702db869e98bbca7ff9ad.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/50df058d467702db869e98bbca7ff9ad.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/50df058d467702db869e98bbca7ff9ad.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为军乐手</h2>为你的队伍鼓舞士气！在自由战吼游戏中，您可以选择成为一名鼓手、笛手或是号手。<strong>演奏那些在历史上真实存在过的经典曲子</strong>；这些曲目均由获奖的艺术家们亲自演奏录制。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过 50 首背景音乐</h2>听一听来自<strong>南卡罗来纳州第二弦乐队</strong>的表演和由美国军乐队演奏的经典曲目。本游戏总共收录了<strong> 57 首</strong>背景音乐，为您的游戏增添色彩，保证不会无聊。<br><br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/838e2b5d34eedf08faf8b3ec87a0b7fc.poster.avif?t=1723617387\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/838e2b5d34eedf08faf8b3ec87a0b7fc.webm?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358710/extras/838e2b5d34eedf08faf8b3ec87a0b7fc.mp4?t=1723617387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内置的地图编辑器</h2>玩腻了游戏预设的地图？别急！自由战吼内置了易于入门且功能丰富的地图编辑器为玩家们创造自己的专属地图。<strong>自定义地图</strong>生成的文件只有几兆大小，在连接服务器时只需几秒钟就能下载到本地，更少等待！尽情游玩！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的管理员工具</h2>在自由战吼中，管理员们可以为服务器订制<strong>超过 120 种功能</strong>。在<strong>游戏内置的界面</strong>里可以轻松调用超过 35 种的快捷管理员工具。如今社区玩家要架设运营管理一个大型服务器要比以往容易许多。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >线列作战</h2>参与到玩家社区中，和其他人一起组织军团（战队）。通过配合和沟通，玩家们可以在游戏中重演美国内战时期经典的线列作战宏大场面。",
